{"tid":2347912,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透：中國監管機構審查螞蟻股權投資　或下令撤投資","createTime":"2020-12-31T11:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T12:44:46.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"832a58876ad16e77ac4de281b06c84c5e56a0005","tid":2347912,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/d8cf51bc05f8bb558914c6d559e99e6520copy_N7hAh_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fd8cf51bc05f8bb558914c6d559e99e6520copy_N7hAh_1200x0.png&h=ed3d2a05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿里巴巴旗下螞蟻集團上市計劃被剎停，隨後亦多次被監管機構約談。據路透社今日（31 日）引述知情人士指，中國監管機構正在審查螞蟻集團，在數十間公司中持有的股權投資，顯示當局有意進一步打擊馬雲的科技金融帝國。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述 3 名消息人士指，中國調查機構正在審查螞蟻集團的股權投資，涉及十多間公司。其中一名知情者指，若果機構發現不公平競爭等違規行為，就有可能要求螞蟻放棄這些投資項目，當中主要都是科技及金融科技初創公司。<br />\n<br />\n另兩名消息人士則指，監管機構正在研究螞蟻在過去幾年的投資，以及這些交易背後的理由及協同效應。一名知情者指，監管機構希望螞蟻脫離一些投資項目，除非其對業務而言是必不可少的。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，一旦螞蟻被強行要求放棄這些投資項目，除了會影響其投資利潤之外，亦會大大削弱螞蟻在金融科技行業的影響力。螞蟻集團的發言人拒絕評論事件，中國證監會亦未有回應查詢。<br />\n<br />\n四大監管機構人民銀行、銀保監會、證監會、外匯局日前約談螞蟻集團，指集團治理機制不健全、藐視監管要求、排斥同業及損害消費者權益等。螞蟻集團的同系公司阿里巴巴則被指涉壟斷行為，遭當局立案調查。華爾街日報日前報道，北京已初步訂出整改螞蟻集團的方案，集團將要重組，中國政府於較賺錢的業務擬取得更大股權，螞蟻最終可能只剩下網上支付業務。"},{"pid":"942ad4846f88ac697d0eb3b17957491858a7252c","tid":2347912,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:10:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/路透-中國監管機構審查螞蟻股權投資-或下令撤投資/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E8%9E%9E%E8%9F%BB%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87-%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%92%A4%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=e45fa18f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E8%9E%9E%E8%9F%BB%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87-%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%92%A4%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%2F&h=163fd504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/路透-中國監管機構審查螞蟻股權投資-或下令撤投資/</a>"},{"pid":"2e043902589ba732baf1187ab7385eda6995fe5f","tid":2347912,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"螞蟻變屎蟲"},{"pid":"e90a96cea3e96d244592be1e4f571ead5af1ca4b","tid":2347912,"uid":321002,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:28:28.000Z","msg":"留番啲蝕既生意俾佢囉，賺既公司全部收歸國有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f286d2ef6311a695641b33526b52f2d054ff59e","tid":2347912,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e90a96cea3e96d244592be1e4f571ead5af1ca4b","tid":2347912,"uid":321002,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:28:28.000Z","msg":"留番啲蝕既生意俾佢囉，賺既公司全部收歸國有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"最後國有唔識做生意，蝕埋攬炒"},{"pid":"83c1e691558edf0cca5ca62311e38a4e6e6bbe73","tid":2347912,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f286d2ef6311a695641b33526b52f2d054ff59e","tid":2347912,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e90a96cea3e96d244592be1e4f571ead5af1ca4b","tid":2347912,"uid":321002,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:28:28.000Z","msg":"留番啲蝕既生意俾佢囉，賺既公司全部收歸國有<img src=\"/assets/fac